    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she\u2019s a total beauty! This car is in truly pristine, showroom-quality shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot. It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always garage-kept, and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019ve been looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for its next adventure, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love for this to go to a great new home!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
