      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours-level condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis is impeccably preserved, featuring documented rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. Power is managed via the factory M-Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The exterior retains its factory depth and gloss, while the interior shows zero bolster compression or trim degradation. Mechanically synchronized and aesthetically flawless, this is a turn-key example for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
