    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'mint' condition. This one-owner masterpiece has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating, entirely free of road rash, stone chips, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine showroom state; the premium hand-stitched leather retains its original scent and supple texture, with absolutely no wear on the bolsters or touchpoints. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist suite, functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule exclusively at the original dealership. With exceptionally low mileage and a fully documented history of care, this vehicle offers the experience of a brand-new delivery. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
